Total / 297 438 / 1 706 / 0.6 / 10.0

Al Hali (Al Hudaydah gov., 12 363 cases, 22 deaths), Bani Al Harith (Amanat Al Asimah gov., 8095 cases, 10 deaths), Ma'ain (Amanat Al Asimah gov., 7 850, 7 deaths) and As Sabain (Amanat Al Asimah gov., 6149 cases, 9 deaths) were still the 4 most affected districts.

